metadata.name: Inner Sanctum I - Muladhara
metadata.description: The seven chakras are the vital energy centers in the human body and each one of them controls a different aspect of our being. When these centers are balanced, we experience a sense of wellbeing and peace. To help bring about this balance, I created "Inner Sanctum"  as a series of digital artworks of one of the seven chakras blossoming into existence.
